net.sf.jameleon.result
Class HttpRequestResult

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.jameleon.result.HttpRequestResult

public class HttpRequestResult
extends java.lang.Object

An implementation of the @see TestResult that represents an HttpRequest. This class keeps track of the resource requested, the function that requested it and the status code returned by the resource.
